23
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:55,330
That's your problem.

24
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:56,410
Fine.

25
00:01:56,510 --> 00:01:57,620
Then wait for my complaint.

26
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:02,980
What's wrong?

27
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,820
Online shops just bully customers now.

28
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,770
I clearly told them I needed an invoice,

29
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,940
then after I paid, they said they couldn't issue it.

30
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:11,450
Why can't they?

31
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,640
I paid with our company's

32
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:14,170
employee welfare gift card.

33
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,010
They said

34
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:16,130
when our company bought the cards,

35
00:02:16,130 --> 00:02:17,570
they had already issued an invoice,

36
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,980
and they can't issue it twice.

37
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,890
Then at least tell me upfront!

38
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,170
If they don't reply by tomorrow,

39
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,500
I'll file a complaint with the Consumers' Association.

40
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:26,980
Will that help?

41
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,340
If you complain to the Consumers' Association,

42
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,820
the seller has to respond.

43
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,010
At least, they need to provide proof

44
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,340
that an invoice was already issued,

45
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,570
plus the relevant laws and rules,

46
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,660
all in writing.

47
