Mr. Pang, is now a good time?

50
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,380
I need to talk to you.

51
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:54,480
Okay.

52
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:55,680
Roof, then.

53
00:02:56,070 --> 00:02:56,570
Sure.

54
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,130
Boss,

55
00:02:59,210 --> 00:03:00,500
can you sign this for me?

56
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:06,410
Okay.

57
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:09,820
I'm heading out.

58
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,500
Okay.

59
00:03:12,460 --> 00:03:15,380
[Zhe]

60
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,730
Dial the number I sent you.

61
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,500
Keep dialing.

62
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,220
Your phone.

63
