I was covering two spots by myself.

284
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,080
Where's Chi?

285
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,940
I'll call him and chew him out.

286
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:48,770
Chi!

287
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,060
Over here!

288
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:55,820
It can't stop!

289
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,370
Dongshan, run!

290
00:15:10,060 --> 00:15:12,460
[Yao "Stinky Foot"]

